		#! // PAYED
		set {_bot_output::%event-guild%::default::embed_payed} to "**Pay:** %discord name of event-member% --> %discord name of arg-1% <:icons8papermoney100:889210789385363576>%nl%```✅  |  You payed %arg-2%💰 to %arg-1%```"
